main event: A sighting of 8-30 objects in a 'V' formation over San Diego, California on 10 April 1956.
interesting points: The objects were observed for two minutes each time,The objects appeared to change positions during the observation,The observer noted the presence of jet aircraft in the area at the same time,There is a suggestion that the sighting could have been generated by birds,This sighting was recorded in a Project 10073 Record Card.
